{"type": "article", "id": 17281, "title": "用手机游戏来玩无人机，这里有一套新玩法", "description": "来一场真实的无人机大战。", "date": "2015-11-09T14:33:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1283, "name": "无人机"}, {"id": 13, "name": "游戏"}, {"id": 18480, "name": "Anima Tecnica s.r.o"}, {"id": 6558, "name": "大疆"}], "category": 4, "author": 73517, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607155514C7MaHjDJexKgkST9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<div>\r\n\t也许你听无人机做灾难救援、空中送货或者视频拍摄听到耳朵都要起茧了。无人机还有另外的玩法，例如说结合手游。最近 <a href=\"http://www.gizmag.com/drone-n-base/40273/\">Anima Technika s.r.o 推出一款小型无人机</a>，专供用户们娱乐消遣使用。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一台游戏无人机 Drone n Base，个小秀气，但暴力的地方在于，它支持最多 8 人在房间里碰撞战斗。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607155513Ov4JbFVanqHE0ozY.jpg\" title=\"Drone n Base 无人机与底座\" alt=\"Drone n Base 无人机与底座\" data-ratio=\"0.49814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><em>Drone n Base 无人机与底座</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\tDrone n Base 可以用手机应用的进行虚拟对战、夺旗飞行等游戏。Drone n Base 和配套的底座上均配有红外感应器，用于为无人机在虚拟场景里定位和无人机操控训练。另外，底座还是一把保护伞，无人机在其附近可免于被攻击。\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t而这些无人机对战起来的效果是这样的：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XMTM4MTYwMTk2NA==/v.swf\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>与商用无人机数千上万的价格相比，<span>Drone n Base</span> </span><a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/drone-n-base-race-battle-drones-at-home#/\">99 美元的 Indiegogo 众筹起价</a><span>也不至于让你钱包那么痛。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来自：<a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-z8LA1vkdFJA/UR2IcuYfW8I/AAAAAAAACO8/oQhYWvQjgKA/s1600/predator-firing-missile4.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">Blogspot</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}